title: DDFP 372: Terrance Knighton & Michael Fabiano
itunes:title: DDFP 372: Terrance Knighton & Michael Fabiano
description:
Shek is joined by Washington Redskins defensive tackle Terrance Knighton (2:22) as they discuss Peyton Manning, his new teammate Robert Griffin III and his favorite movies. Then, NFL Fantasy Live’s Michael Fabiano visits Shek (18:00) to debate who should go in the first round of your fantasy draft and who has sneaky fantasy potential in 2015.   

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
